description: ClashRoyaleHelper responds to user's query about the description to the card of Clash Royale. User can say something like "can you tell me something about a knight?", the app will gives description to that card.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask game helper for clash royale can you tell me something about a knight
Alexa, ask game helper for clash royale what is a golem
Alexa, ask game helper for clash royale can you tell me something about the witch
imageAltText: Game Helper for Clash Royale icon
name: Game Helper for Clash Royale
shortDescription: ClashRoyaleHelper responds to user's query about the description to the card of Clash Royale.
